extendedInfo.description: Pass Safe Free 2 is a password manager for Android. With Pass Safe Free 2 you can have all your passwords in one place, protected by a master password, so you'll never lose a password again. All passwords are stored locally on the phone, encrypted so only Pass Safe Free 2 can read them.IMPORTANT NOTE:THIS APPLICATION REQUIRES INTERNET CONNECTION IN ORDER TO GET AND DISPLAY THE ADS. THIS APPLICATION WILL NOT SEND YOUR PASSWORDS TO THE DEVELOPER OR ANYWHERE ELSE. IF YOU STILL DO NOT TRUST IT, YOU CAN BUY THE PAID VERSION, WHICH DOES NOT REQUEST INTERNET CONNECTION BECAUSE IT'S ADD FREE.This is a free version, supported by ads. If you like it and you want to support the developer, please consider the paid version. Except for the ads, there is no difference between the paid and the free version.KW: Android Password Manager, Password Safe, Save Password, Store Password, Manage Passwords, Password, Manager
